sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant Domain as Configuration
    participant History as ConfigurationHistory
    participant DB as Database
    participant Cache as Redis
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: PUT /api/v1/admin/configurations/{id}
    Note right of Client: {value: "15"}

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract configId and value
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create UpdateConfigValueCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check value is valid format
    Validator->>Validator: Verify admin role
    Validator->>DB: Check config exists
    DB-->>Validator: Config found ✓
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get Configuration
    DB-->>Handler: Configuration (Key: "RAG:DefaultTopK", Value: "10")

    Handler->>History: Create history record
    History->>History: Version = current version
    History->>History: Value = old value
    History->>History: ChangedAt = UtcNow

    Handler->>Domain: config.UpdateValue("15")
    Domain->>Domain: Value = "15"
    Domain->>Domain: Version++
    Domain->>Domain: UpdatedAt = UtcNow
    Domain->>Events: Raise ConfigurationUpdatedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(config, history)
    DB-->>Handler: Saved ✓

    Handler->>Cache: InvalidateKey("config:RAG:DefaultTopK")
    Cache-->>Handler: Cache invalidated ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish ConfigurationUpdatedEvent
    Note over Events: All services receive update
    Events->>Events: Broadcast to subscribers

    Handler-->>Mediator: ConfigurationDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: ConfigurationDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {id, key, value: "15", version: 2}
